public class LegalEntity extends net.tangly.core.MutableEntityExtendedImp implements net.tangly.core.MutableEntityExtended, CrmEntity
A legal entity is a legally recognized organization able to underwrite contracts and hire employees. A legal entity has a name, an identity defined as the legal identifier of an organization (e.g., zefix UID number in Switzerland, EUID in Europe), and a text describing it.
